<div class="image-caption">Init with Values...</div>

<p>I’ll be covering parameter modulation and hardware controllers in the next 2 posts. It may seem weird to bunch these things together, but in FLStudio they are linked (pun intended) together.</p>

<p>I’m going to spoil this article a bit, and tell you that this is one of FLStudio’s strong points. Somehow I rarely see people talking about it, or see it used in projects.</p>

<p>Get ready to get modulated!</p>

